name: Joukon Seikkailut in the Magical Wonderland of Ilimajoki
name_original: Joukon Seikkailut in the Magical Wonderland of Ilimajoki
description: Simple game I made as my very first Unity project in school 2021. You control this dude named Jouko in the center of Ilmajoki and your job is to catch your cows that have run away.
